OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed after mum and son
OL,4,Cattacked during knifepoint burglary
OL,6,FA 20-year-old man has been jailed
OL,7,Ffollowing a knifepoint burglary in .
OL,9,FJack Nottle, 20, of Hampstead Terrace,
OL,10,Fwas sentenced at Truro Crown Court on
OL,11,F23 February to four and a half years
OL,12,Fin a young offenders' institution
OL,13,Fafter pleading guilty to aggravated
OL,14,Fburglary.
OL,16,FOfficers were called to a home in
OL,17,FFurze Hill, Bodmin, on 24 August to
OL,18,Freports of three masked men dressed in
OL,19,Fblack assaulting people in the
OL,20,Fproperty.
