OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed after mum and son
OL,4,Cattacked during knifepoint burglary
OL,6,FThe other suspects were never traced.
OL,8,FBoth victims - the mother and son -
OL,9,Fsustained suspected knife wounds and
OL,10,Frequired hospital treatment.
OL,12,FOn the night of the attack, three men
OL,13,Fentered the property through a back
OL,14,Fdoor and went upstairs into one of the
OL,15,Fbedrooms.
OL,17,FPolice say the mother tried to
OL,18,Fintervene in an attack on her son, and
OL,19,Fwas injured in the process.
