OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed after mum and son
OL,4,Cattacked during knifepoint burglary
OL,6,FThe son recalled demands being made
OL,7,Ffor money while a knife was held to
OL,8,Fhim and #200-300 taken from his wallet.
OL,10,FAround #500 also went missing from a
OL,11,Fdrawer in the house.
OL,13,FThe son sustained cuts to the left arm
OL,14,Fand chest area, while the mum suffered
OL,15,Fa hand injury which required surgery.
OL,17,FShortly after, police attended an
OL,18,Faddress in Bodmin and arrested Nottle.
OL,19,FThey also searched his property and
OL,20,Fseized clothing, trainers, a wallet
OL,21,Fcontaining money and a phone.
