OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed after mum and son
OL,4,Cattacked during knifepoint burglary
OL,6,FOfficers also found a large "Rambo"
OL,7,Fstyle knife on top of a fuse box.
OL,9,FNottle pleaded guilty to the burglary
OL,10,Fafter the discovery of the knife and
OL,11,Fthe forensics tracing to the scene.
OL,13,FPolice say, while swabs were being
OL,14,Ftaken in his cell, Nottle asked
OL,15,Fofficers: "Am I the only one that's
OL,16,Fbeen arrested?"
OL,18,FThe other two suspects were never
OL,19,Fidentified.
