OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed after mum and son
OL,4,Cattacked during knifepoint burglary
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Northcott from
OL,7,Fsaid: "In recent times, Bodmin has
OL,8,Fseen its share of crime where
OL,9,Foffenders carry knives in order to
OL,10,Finstil fear on others or inflict
OL,11,Fserious harm.
OL,13,F"Those involved in this aggravated
OL,14,Fburglary have entered a family home
OL,15,Fwith the intention of causing harm to
OL,16,Fthose inside whilst armed with a knife.
OL,18,F"This is not acceptable and will not
OL,19,Fonly have affected the victims but
OL,20,Falso the wider community.
