OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed after mum and son
OL,4,Cattacked during knifepoint burglary
OL,6,F"The actions of police officers
OL,7,Fattending this incident allowed for
OL,8,Fkey evidence to be obtained to support
OL,9,Fthis investigation including the
OL,10,Frecovery of a knife from circulation
OL,11,Fthat the offenders had no lawful or
OL,12,Flogical reason to possess.
OL,14,F"In cases such as this, it is
OL,15,Fimportant for victims and witnesses to
OL,16,Fcome forward and I commend those
OL,17,Finvolved in this case for their
OL,18,Fcommitment to this investigation.
