OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed after mum and son
OL,4,Cattacked during knifepoint burglary
OL,6,F"The sentencing in this case should
OL,7,Fact as a deterrent to those choosing
OL,8,Fto carry knives and also provide some
OL,9,Freassurance to the community that
OL,10,Fpeople carrying knives will be pursued
OL,11,Fby police and that the courts will
OL,12,Fhand down immediate custodial
OL,13,Fsentences to those found guilty."
